Uicheon Doryonggi.Description: Treasured sabre belongs to a dragon and commands an army of beasts. If the Heaven Sword does not come out, then who will fight for mastery. An ignorant brat, Zhang Wuji, grew up on a lonely island. He got lucky out of a bad situation and became a well known CEO, married a rich beauty, and lived a life of pretending. Who wants to be a supreme being of the martial arts world? Having the protagonist aura is the most important!
